Packages 
Package Description
cf.lukasheinzl.crypto
This package contains classes used to do encryption / decryption of data
cf.lukasheinzl.graph
This package contains the Node as a base node class for the algorithms in the cf.lukasheinzl.graph.algorithm package
cf.lukasheinzl.graph.algorithm
This package contains the algorithms used to find paths through node graphs Uses Node as a base node class
cf.lukasheinzl.lexing
This package contains a lexer API for file parsing.
cf.lukasheinzl.parsing
This package conatins classes and interfaces for parsing Tokens from the cf.lukasheinzl.lexing package.
cf.lukasheinzl.syntax
This package contains an API for syntax highlighting.
cf.lukasheinzl.syntax.lang
This package contains predefined formatters for various programming languages.
cf.lukasheinzl.util
This package contains useful classes additional to Java's Class Library and Wrappers over a few Java APIs.
